ur trade resource will use HTTP methods as follows:
HTTP Method	URI	                                 Action
GET	http://[hostname]/todo/api/v1.0/trade	        |Retrieve list of trade
GET	http://[hostname]/todo/api/v1.0/trade/[trade_id]|Retrieve a trade
POST	http://[hostname]/todo/api/v1.0/trade	        |Create a new trade
PUT	http://[hostname]/todo/api/v1.0/trade/[trade_id]|Update an existing trade
DELETE	http://[hostname]/todo/api/v1.0/trade/[trade_id]|Delete a trade


We can define a trade as having the following fields:

    id: unique identifier for trade. Numeric type.
    title: short trade description. String type.
    description: long trade description. Text type.
    done: trade completion state. Boolean type.


